{"tid":598823,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"古天樂對香港電影的貢獻係咪已經超越左劉德華？","createTime":"2018-03-20T01:11:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-20T09:09:10.000Z","uid":149494,"like":49,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ac48ea6c0ca0e801526e30a03a2da217df9bb45a","tid":598823,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T01:11:22.000Z","msg":"講真，兩個都拍過好多戲，大部份都爛片<br />\n但劉華成日比人話對香港電影有貢獻都係因為佢肯投資下d小本電影,幫下新晉導演<br />\n但其實有好多都係強國導演黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家古仔唔止投資小本電影,仲玩埋大製作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又真係全力支持香港既電影人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係一下就超越哂劉華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw,諗起幾年前條on9佬謝霆鋒講到自己間公司對電影業幾有貢獻咁,相比之下根本係白痴仔一名<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dadb05992945dde239e2e296314af7762ca20b6a","tid":598823,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":12,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T01:12:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c1c6c23b12795dbfc455f43f5f81e91a4e3a989","tid":598823,"uid":149494,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T01:23:55.000Z","msg":"仲要古仔低調好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n劉華好似成日要身邊d人吹奏佢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f19320c05a37426bb782934097add36cdf2ac07a","tid":598823,"uid":172407,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T01:26:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢首今期流行對香港仲大貢獻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac893de39b0e0b73ee690e4fa817598e52ca5df","tid":598823,"uid":131259,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T01:29: